							<h4>FOUNDER AND DIRECTOR</h4>
							
							<h2>Andy Garner</h2>
							
							<p>Andy has over 20 years of software development experience across many market sectors including, technology, retail, hospitality financial services and engineering. He has worked for globally recognised companies that lead their market sectors. These include Just Eat, ASOS, Capita and Microsoft.</p>
<p>As a founding Partner at Elastic Mint Andy is experienced at leading large teams of developers on behalf of clients as well as tackling complex software development challenges on his own as required.</p>
<p>Andy is particularly adept at leading complex bespoke software programmes to ensure the business requirement is delivered on time and in full. He is also a strong advocate in sharing knowledge with clients and bringing on less experienced members of their team so that they have the skills to continue developing and maintaining what is built.</p>
							
